This paper discusses the use of artificial neural networks for Entity Classification and Relation Extraction in order to automatically populate a person ontology graph from unstructured data. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CL (Computation and Language), which are both focused on natural language processing and machine learning. The paper also mentions the use of neural models, which suggests that cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses the creation of a dataset, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.DB (Databases).
